display_long_description:
A new type of 2.5D jet fighter dogfight shooting game!
 Brilliant omnidirectional scrolling side view type!
 You can play offline, free, easy and full of fun!
 Wipe out the ferocious waves of attacks and conquer the stage!

★How to play★ 
Destroy all enemies to clear the stage. In all 24 stages, the enemy's attack power will increase from the second week onwards.

Touch the central controller to control your own fighter.

Your fighter will not take damage if it collides with an enemy, but it will take damage if the altitude is below 0m.

On the title screen, you can select from cleared laps and stages. Red letters are laps and stages that will continue. If you select a lap and stage other than continuation, the score will be reset to 0 and remaining lives will be reset to 3.

★Story★ 
In the year 202X AD, a lone professional fighter pilot was fighting to defeat a rebel force. People call him "Jet Shooter". They continue to use their high-performance fighter planes to engage in battles that governments around the world cannot openly engage in...

Music: Maoudamashii

Copyright 2022ｰNam Creations
